Title: MS 17 folio 1
Description.abstract: 1. ff. 1-10v [text begins with heading/opening sentence in top margin of f. 1 added by the hand of the text] Criminosus criminosum accusare non potest / [text block] excipiuntur papa et imperator qui non habent iudices ...

Title: MS 17 folio 11
Description.abstract: 2. ff. 11-12v: [abbreviated Hours of the Cross, written in a formal textura but with the heading added in the cramped cursive of ff. 1-10v] Incipunt hore sancte crucis. Domine labia mea apperies. Deus in aiutorium. Christum captum ... Vidimus Ihesum Christum propter passionem mortis sue gloria et honore coronatum ut gratia dei pro notis gustaret mortem. Deo gratias.
